       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI10502.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI10502.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Balan蔞 do Projecto                                        *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI10502         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3606 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5013 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6702 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD4805 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5101 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5305 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV1050.
       COPY COCV1051.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT3606 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3606'.
           05 CON-COVT5013 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT5013'.
           05 CON-COVT6702 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6702'.
           05 CON-COVT4805 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT4805'.
           05 CON-COVT5101 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT5101'.
           05 CON-COVT5305 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT5305'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI10502'.
           05 WS-SERVICOS         PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-DESPESAS         PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-OUTROS           PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-LIQUIDADAS       PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-PORLIQUIDAR      PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-VENCIDAS         PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-SALDESPFORN      PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-SALDESPCOLAB     PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-SALHORAS         PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-VALOR1           PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-SALVALOR         PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-SALGLOBAL        PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-TOTALHORAS       PIC  S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-FACTURA          PIC  X(02) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NCREDITO         PIC  X(02) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CSTATUS-EMIT     PIC  X(01) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CSTATUS-PPAG     PIC  X(01) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CSTATUS-PAG      PIC  X(01) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CSTATUS-ANUL     PIC  X(01) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CSTATUS-CANC     PIC  X(01) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CTIPFAC-SERVICOS PIC  X(02) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CTIPFAC-DESPESAS PIC  X(02) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DATA-HOJE        PIC  X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CSTATDP-RECB     PIC  X(02) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CSTATDP-PAG      PIC  X(02) VALUE SPACES.

      ******************************************************************
      * DB2
      ******************************************************************

           EXEC SQL
            DECLARE CURCOT51 CURSOR FOR
             SELECT CIDEMP
                  , GNOMEEMP
                  , DTPROC
                  , DTMESANO
                  , GPAIS
                  , GEMPRESA
                  , CIDPROJ
                  , GPROJ
                  , ZHORAS
               FROM COVT5101_TIMEREPT
              WHERE CIDPROJ   = :COCD5101-CIDPROJ
           END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI10502         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA'    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT      TO COCV1050-MSG.
           MOVE COCV1050-ASE                 TO COCV1051-ASE.
           MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I     TO WS-DATA-HOJE.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1050-ADE       TO COCV1051-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2500-VALIDACOES
                 THRU 2500-VALIDACOES-EXIT
           END-IF

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-OBTEM-DADOS
                 THRU 2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-OBTEM-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OBTEM-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO       TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO.

      *--- Budget
           MOVE COCD3606-NBUDGET           TO COCV1051-BUDGET.

      *--- Factura誽o de Servi蔞s
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2110-FAC-SERV
                 THRU 2110-FAC-SERV-EXIT
           END-IF.
           MOVE WS-SERVICOS                TO COCV1051-SERVICOS.

      *--- Factura誽o de Despesas
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2120-FAC-DESP
                 THRU 2120-FAC-DESP-EXIT
           END-IF.
           MOVE WS-DESPESAS                TO COCV1051-DESPESAS.

      *--- Factura誽o de Outros
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2130-FAC-OUTR
                 THRU 2130-FAC-OUTR-EXIT
           END-IF.
           MOVE WS-OUTROS                  TO COCV1051-OUTROS.

      *--- Factura誽o Liquidadas
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2140-FAC-LIQU
                 THRU 2140-FAC-LIQU-EXIT
           END-IF.
           MOVE WS-LIQUIDADAS              TO COCV1051-LIQUIDADAS.

      *--- Factura誽o Por Liquidar
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2150-FAC-PLIQ
                 THRU 2150-FAC-PLIQ-EXIT
           END-IF.
           MOVE WS-PORLIQUIDAR             TO COCV1051-PORLIQUIDAR.

      *--- Factura誽o Vencidas
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2160-FAC-VENC
                 THRU 2160-FAC-VENC-EXIT
           END-IF.
           MOVE WS-VENCIDAS                TO COCV1051-VENCIDAS.

      *--- Saldo Despesas Fornecedores
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2170-DSP-FRNC
                 THRU 2170-DSP-FRNC-EXIT
           END-IF.
           MOVE WS-SALDESPFORN             TO COCV1051-SALDESPFORN.

      *--- Saldo Despesas Colaboradores
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2180-DSP-COLB
                 THRU 2180-DSP-COLB-EXIT
           END-IF.
           MOVE WS-SALDESPCOLAB            TO COCV1051-SALDESPCOLAB.

      *--- Saldo de Horas
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2190-HORAS
                 THRU 2190-HORAS-EXIT
           END-IF.
           MOVE WS-SALHORAS                TO COCV1051-SALHORAS.

      *--- Saldo de Valor
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2195-VALOR
                 THRU 2195-VALOR-EXIT
           END-IF.
           MOVE WS-SALVALOR                TO COCV1051-SALVALOR.

      *--- Saldo Global
           COMPUTE WS-SALGLOBAL = ( WS-SERVICOS
                                +   WS-DESPESAS
                                +   WS-OUTROS       )
                                - ( WS-SALDESPFORN
                                +   WS-SALDESPCOLAB
                                +   WS-SALVALOR     ).
           MOVE WS-SALGLOBAL               TO COCV1051-SALGLOBAL.

       2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2500-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-VALIDACOES   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2510-LER-PROJECTO THRU 2510-LER-PROJECTO-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2500-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2510-LER-PROJECTO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2510-LER-PROJECTO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2510-LER-PROJECTO ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO TO COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT NIDPROJECTO
                      , CPROJECT
                      , CLIENTE
                      , LINHANEG
                      , RESPONS
                      , NBUDGET
                 INTO  :COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO
                    ,  :COCD3606-CPROJECT
                    ,  :COCD3606-CLIENTE
                    ,  :COCD3606-LINHANEG
                    ,  :COCD3606-RESPONS
                    ,  :COCD3606-NBUDGET
                 FROM COVT3606_PROJECTS
                 WHERE NIDPROJECTO = :COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT3606
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF DB2-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-S
              MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

       2510-LER-PROJECTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2110-FAC-SERV
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2110-FAC-SERV.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2110-FAC-SERV     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *
           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCK0002-CTIPFAC-SERVICOS TO COCD5013-CTIPFAC.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-CANC     TO WS-CSTATUS-CANC.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-ANUL     TO WS-CSTATUS-ANUL.
           MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA          TO WS-FACTURA.
           MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO     TO WS-NCREDITO.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT IFNULL(SUM(NTOTALAMOUNT), 0)
                  , IFNULL(SUM(NTOTNCR), 0)
               INTO :COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                  , :COCD5013-NTOTNCR
               FROM COVT5013_INVOICES
              WHERE      NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                AND      CTIPFAC     = :COCD5013-CTIPFAC
                AND  (   CTIPDOC     = :WS-FACTURA
                 OR      CTIPDOC     = :WS-NCREDITO )
                AND    ( CSTATUS    <> :WS-CSTATUS-ANUL
                AND      CSTATUS    <> :WS-CSTATUS-CANC)
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5013 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 COMPUTE WS-SERVICOS = COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                                     - COCD5013-NTOTNCR
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                  MOVE ZEROES               TO WS-SERVICOS
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2110-FAC-SERV-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2120-FAC-DESP
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2120-FAC-DESP.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2120-FAC-DESP     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *
           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCK0002-CTIPFAC-DESPESAS TO COCD5013-CTIPFAC.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-EMIT     TO WS-CSTATUS-EMIT.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PPAG     TO WS-CSTATUS-PPAG.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG      TO WS-CSTATUS-PAG.
           MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA          TO WS-FACTURA.
           MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO     TO WS-NCREDITO.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT IFNULL(SUM(NTOTALAMOUNT), 0)
                  , IFNULL(SUM(NTOTNCR), 0)
               INTO :COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                  , :COCD5013-NTOTNCR
               FROM COVT5013_INVOICES
              WHERE (    NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                AND      CTIPDOC     = :WS-FACTURA
                AND      CTIPFAC     = :COCD5013-CTIPFAC
                AND    ( CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-EMIT
                OR       CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-PPAG
                OR       CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-PAG  )     )

                OR  (    NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                AND      CTIPDOC     = :WS-NCREDITO
                AND      CTIPFAC     = :COCD5013-CTIPFAC      )
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5013 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 COMPUTE WS-DESPESAS = COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                                     - COCD5013-NTOTNCR
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                  MOVE ZEROES               TO WS-DESPESAS
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2120-FAC-DESP-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2130-FAC-OUTR
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2130-FAC-OUTR.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2130-FAC-OUTR     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *
           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCK0002-CTIPFAC-SERVICOS TO WS-CTIPFAC-SERVICOS.
           MOVE COCK0002-CTIPFAC-DESPESAS TO WS-CTIPFAC-DESPESAS.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-EMIT     TO WS-CSTATUS-EMIT.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PPAG     TO WS-CSTATUS-PPAG.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG      TO WS-CSTATUS-PAG.
           MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA          TO WS-FACTURA.
           MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO     TO WS-NCREDITO.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT IFNULL(SUM(NTOTALAMOUNT), 0)
                  , IFNULL(SUM(NTOTNCR), 0)
               INTO :COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                  , :COCD5013-NTOTNCR
               FROM COVT5013_INVOICES
              WHERE (    NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                AND      CTIPDOC     = :WS-FACTURA
                AND    ( CTIPFAC    <> :WS-CTIPFAC-SERVICOS
                AND      CTIPFAC    <> :WS-CTIPFAC-DESPESAS )
                AND    ( CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-EMIT
                OR       CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-PPAG
                OR       CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-PAG  )     )

                OR  (    NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                AND      CTIPDOC     = :WS-NCREDITO
                AND    ( CTIPFAC    <> :WS-CTIPFAC-SERVICOS
                AND      CTIPFAC    <> :WS-CTIPFAC-DESPESAS )
                AND    ( CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-EMIT
                OR       CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-PPAG
                OR       CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-PAG  )     )
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5013 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 COMPUTE WS-OUTROS   = COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                                     - COCD5013-NTOTNCR
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                  MOVE ZEROES               TO WS-OUTROS
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2130-FAC-OUTR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2140-FAC-LIQU
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2140-FAC-LIQU.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2140-FAC-LIQU     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *
           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG      TO WS-CSTATUS-PAG.
           MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA          TO WS-FACTURA.
           MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO     TO WS-NCREDITO.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT IFNULL(SUM(NTOTALAMOUNT), 0)
                  , IFNULL(SUM(NTOTNCR), 0)
               INTO :COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                  , :COCD5013-NTOTNCR
               FROM COVT5013_INVOICES
              WHERE (    NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                AND      CTIPDOC     = :WS-FACTURA
                AND      CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-PAG       )

                OR  (    NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                AND      CTIPDOC     = :WS-NCREDITO
                AND      CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-PAG        )
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5013 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 COMPUTE WS-LIQUIDADAS = COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                                       - COCD5013-NTOTNCR
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                  MOVE ZEROES               TO WS-LIQUIDADAS
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2140-FAC-LIQU-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2150-FAC-PLIQ
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2150-FAC-PLIQ.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2150-FAC-PLIQ     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *
           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO.

           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-CANC     TO WS-CSTATUS-CANC.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-ANUL     TO WS-CSTATUS-ANUL.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG      TO WS-CSTATUS-PAG.

           MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA          TO WS-FACTURA.
           MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO     TO WS-NCREDITO.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT IFNULL(SUM(NTOTALAMOUNT), 0)
                  , IFNULL(SUM(NTOTNCR), 0)
               INTO :COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                  , :COCD5013-NTOTNCR
               FROM COVT5013_INVOICES
              WHERE      NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                AND      CSTATUS    <> :WS-CSTATUS-ANUL
                AND      CSTATUS    <> :WS-CSTATUS-PAG
                AND      CSTATUS    <> :WS-CSTATUS-CANC

                AND    ( CTIPDOC     = :WS-NCREDITO
                 OR      CTIPDOC     = :WS-FACTURA )
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5013 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 COMPUTE WS-PORLIQUIDAR = COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                                        - COCD5013-NTOTNCR
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                  MOVE ZEROES               TO WS-PORLIQUIDAR
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2150-FAC-PLIQ-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2160-FAC-VENC
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2160-FAC-VENC.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2160-FAC-VENC     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *
           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-EMIT     TO WS-CSTATUS-EMIT.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PPAG     TO WS-CSTATUS-PPAG.
           MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA          TO WS-FACTURA.
           MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO     TO WS-NCREDITO.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT IFNULL(SUM(NTOTALAMOUNT), 0)
                  , IFNULL(SUM(NTOTNCR), 0)
               INTO :COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                  , :COCD5013-NTOTNCR
               FROM COVT5013_INVOICES
              WHERE (    NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                AND      CTIPDOC     = :WS-FACTURA
                AND      DDATEDUE    < :WS-DATA-HOJE
                AND    ( CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-EMIT
                OR       CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-PPAG )     )

                OR  (    NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                AND      CTIPDOC     = :WS-NCREDITO
                AND      DDATEDUE    < :WS-DATA-HOJE
                AND    ( CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-EMIT
                AND      CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATUS-PPAG )     )
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5013 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 COMPUTE WS-VENCIDAS    = COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                                        - COCD5013-NTOTNCR
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                  MOVE ZEROES               TO WS-VENCIDAS
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2160-FAC-VENC-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2170-DSP-FRNC
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2170-DSP-FRNC.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2170-DSP-FRNC     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *
           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD6702-PROJDSP.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATDP-PAG      TO WS-CSTATDP-PAG.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT IFNULL(SUM(NTOTALAMOUNT), 0)
               INTO :COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
               FROM COVT6702_EXPENSES
              WHERE   PROJDSP     = :COCD6702-PROJDSP
                AND   CSTATUS     = :WS-CSTATDP-PAG
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6702 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT TO WS-SALDESPFORN
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                  MOVE ZEROES               TO WS-SALDESPFORN
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2170-DSP-FRNC-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2180-DSP-COLB
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2180-DSP-COLB.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2180-DSP-COLB     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *
           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD4805-CIDPROJ.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT IFNULL(SUM(MVLR), 0)
                  , IFNULL(SUM(NVALKMS), 0)
               INTO :COCD4805-MVLR
                  , :COCD4805-NVALKMS
               FROM COVT4805_EXPENSE
              WHERE   CIDPROJ     = :COCD4805-CIDPROJ
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT4805 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 COMPUTE WS-SALDESPCOLAB = COCD4805-MVLR
                                         + COCD4805-NVALKMS
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                  MOVE ZEROES               TO WS-SALDESPCOLAB
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2180-DSP-COLB-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2190-HORAS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2190-HORAS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2190-HORAS        ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *
           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD5101-CIDPROJ.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT IFNULL(SUM(ZHORAS), 0)
               INTO :WS-TOTALHORAS
               FROM COVT5101_TIMEREPT
              WHERE   CIDPROJ     = :COCD5101-CIDPROJ
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5101 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                  MOVE WS-TOTALHORAS        TO WS-SALHORAS
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                  MOVE ZEROES               TO WS-SALHORAS
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV1051-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2190-HORAS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2195-VALOR
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2195-VALOR.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2195-VALOR        ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2020-OPEN
                 THRU 2029-OPEN-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2030-FETCH
                 THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 PERFORM 2040-CONTINUA
                    THRU 2049-CONTINUA-EXIT
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2070-CLOSE
              THRU 2079-CLOSE-EXIT.

       2195-VALOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2020-OPEN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2020-OPEN.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE ZEROS                   TO WS-SALVALOR.
           MOVE COCV1050-NIDPROJECTO    TO COCD5101-CIDPROJ.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             OPEN CURCOT51
           END-EXEC.
      *
           MOVE CON-COVT5101               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
       2029-OPEN-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2030-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2030-FETCH.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2030-FETCH' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           EXEC SQL
              FETCH CURCOT51
              INTO  :COCD5101-CIDEMP
                  , :COCD5101-GNOMEEMP
                  , :COCD5101-DTPROC
                  , :COCD5101-DTMESANO
                  , :COCD5101-GPAIS
                  , :COCD5101-GEMPRESA
                  , :COCD5101-CIDPROJ
                  , :COCD5101-GPROJ
                  , :COCD5101-ZHORAS
           END-EXEC.
      *
           MOVE CON-COVT5101               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
       2039-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2040-CONTINUA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2040-CONTINUA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2040-CONTINUA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           PERFORM 2050-TRATA-OCCURS
              THRU 2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT
                UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                   OR NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS.
      *
       2049-CONTINUA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2050-TRATA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-TRATA-OCCURS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
             MOVE '2050-TRATA-OCCURS'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
             PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           PERFORM 2061-LER-COT53 THRU 2061-LER-COT53.
           COMPUTE WS-VALOR1   = COCD5101-ZHORAS * COCD5305-CCUSTO.
           COMPUTE WS-SALVALOR = WS-SALVALOR + WS-VALOR1.
      *
           PERFORM 2030-FETCH
              THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT.
      *
       2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2061-LER-COT53
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2061-LER-COT53.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2061-LER-COT53' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE COCD5101-CIDEMP  TO COCD5305-NTRABALHADOR.
      *
           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT
                       ZCUNICO
                     , GNOME
                     , NTRABALHADOR
                     , CCUSTO
                 INTO
                       :COCD5305-ZCUNICO
                     , :COCD5305-GNOME
                     , :COCD5305-NTRABALHADOR
                     , :COCD5305-CCUSTO
                 FROM COVT5305_PESSOAS
                 WHERE
                    NTRABALHADOR = :COCD5305-NTRABALHADOR
           END-EXEC.
      *
           MOVE CON-COVT5305
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 CONTINUE
              ELSE
                 MOVE ZEROS
                   TO COCD5305-CCUSTO
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
       2061-LER-COT53-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2070-CLOSE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2070-CLOSE.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2070-CLOSE' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           EXEC SQL
               CLOSE CURCOT51
           END-EXEC.
      *
       2079-CLOSE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1051-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV1051-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV1051-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
